ASSISTED BY OFFICE OFFICIALS WHO ACT AS GOAL JUDGES TIME KEEPERS AND 
OFFICIAL SCORERS THE MOST WIDESPREAD SYSTEM IN USE TODAY IS THE THREEMAN 
SYSTEM THAT USES ONE REFEREE AND TWO LINESMEN ANOTHER LESS COMMONLY USED 
