JANUARY ICE HOCKEY IS A FULL CONTACT SPORT AND CARRIES A HIGH RISK OF 
INJURY PLAYERS ARE MOVING AT SPEEDS AROUND APPROXIMATELY MPH AND QUITE A 
BIT OF THE GAME REVOLVES AROUND THE PHYSICAL CONTACT BETWEEN THE PLAYERS 
SKATE BLADES HOCKEY STICKS SHOULDERS HIPS AND HOCKEY PUCKS ALL CONTRIBUTE 
